title: Total.War.ROME.II-RELOADED PATCH
description:
Total.War.ROME.II-RELOADED PATCH - -nelly-
                     ==========================================


1. Copy and paste TWR PATCH into Total.War.ROME.II-RELOADED program installation directory. Normally located at:



x64bit operating systems:
=========================


C:Program Files (x86)Total War ROME II


x86(x32bit) operating systems:
==============================


C:Program FilesTotal War ROME II


2. Right click on TWR PATCH and select "Run as administrator".
3. Click on the PATCH TAB.
4. When patching completes, click on the EXIT TAB and delete TWR PATCH.

JOB DONE!!!
